Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.97,0:00:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will now explain the parameters
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.75,0:00:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of the final mission, Operation Skuld.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.66,0:00:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Change the result without changing \Nthe established past.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.00,0:00:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The past consists of Makise Kurisu, \Nlying in a bloody pool,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.72,0:00:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Okabe Rintarou seeing her there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.98,0:00:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Change the past without changing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.53,0:00:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, pass me that screwdriver.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.12,0:00:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you calling me "Dad"?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.77,0:00:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.63,0:00:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought. We only get one more trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.09,0:00:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have enough fuel for more than \None trip to the past and back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.29,0:00:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you won't be able to return to the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.28,0:00:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never planned to.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.46,0:00:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By changing the world line here,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,thus changing the future, I won't need to go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.59,0:00:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.71,0:01:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I fail to change it, I'll have to stay here...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.80,0:01:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regretting it, forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.26,0:01:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.30,0:01:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.72,0:01:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not your uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.33,0:01:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Hououin Kyouma, mad scientist,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.37,0:01:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the man who will destroy \Nthe world's ruling structure.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.53,0:01:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Failure is not an option...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.43,0:01:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it. I believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.11,0:01:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We commence Operation Skuld...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.39,0:01:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time is now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.60,0:03:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.47,0:03:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it was around here somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.02,0:03:18.47,Title1,,0000,0000,0000,,Achievement Point
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.47,0:03:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He made me LOL when he said, "The time is now,"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.18,0:03:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but immediately had to run to the lab \Nbecause he forgot something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.86,0:03:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.32,0:03:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't leave the time machine \Nthere for too long...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.97,0:03:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Cyalume Saber?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.81,0:03:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.37,0:03:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sticky red liquid of its core is the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.63,0:03:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I didn't know that was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.72,0:03:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.84,0:03:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You plan to substitute it for Makise Kurisu's blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.07,0:03:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.31,0:03:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On July 28th, if I see
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.85,0:04:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,an unconscious Christina, lying in a pool of blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the past won't change.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.30,0:04:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the idea behind Operation Skuld.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.14,0:04:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it makes sense, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.07,0:04:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it seem a little too easy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.26,0:04:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Future Okarin sounded like a \Nlarger secret was at work here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.04,0:04:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hououin Kyouma speaks ever more dramatically,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.02,0:04:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when a plan is simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.29,0:04:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.54,0:04:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see through his schemes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.85,0:04:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know whether to be impressed or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.76,0:04:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mad scientist fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.36,0:04:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.14,0:04:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.58,0:04:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did that Kurisu-san person sit here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.02,0:04:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.49,0:04:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'd get really excited and talk to Daru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.01,0:04:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Mayushii wouldn't really understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.48,0:04:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they were having lots of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.80,0:05:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you two fought constantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.35,0:05:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but really, you were good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayushii, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.06,0:05:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Makise Kurisu is a scientific genius...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.06,0:05:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'd never come to a lab like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.31,0:05:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's weird, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.98,0:05:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she possesses the Reading Steiner, also?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.64,0:05:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.64,0:05:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But somewhere inside, she remembers
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.02,0:05:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what happened in the other world lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.97,0:05:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone does, somewhere in their hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.07,0:05:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurisu did everything she could to save Mayuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.65,0:05:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri... No, all of us can be here now
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.80,0:05:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because of Kurisu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.91,0:05:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Okarin? Do you like Kurisu-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.76,0:05:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Christina is my assistant, my dear friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.27,0:05:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and very special to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.22,0:06:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.02,0:06:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she's in love with me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.29,0:06:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Okarin gets a real girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.27,0:06:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, you have to save her,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.03,0:06:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.49,0:06:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.70,0:06:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.15,0:06:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be sure to bring her back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.52,0:06:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.84,0:06:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, um... Miss Amane...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.44,0:06:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're really my daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.92,0:06:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who was my bride?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.34,0:06:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep that a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.45,0:06:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.09,0:06:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.71,0:07:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've managed to arrive at \Nexactly the same time as before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.65,0:07:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest is up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.56,0:07:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.76,0:07:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave the Cyalume Saber where I asked you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.30,0:07:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.69,0:07:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Change the result without changing \Nthe established past...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.87,0:07:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For that to work...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.30,0:07:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...this is where I begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.20,0:07:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know the overall effect,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.12,0:07:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but if I get the metal Upa here,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it diminishes the odds of \Nany metal ending up in that folder.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.08,0:07:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.39,0:07:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't many left of this series,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.22,0:07:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Mayushii's out of hundred-yen coins!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.95,0:08:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be a spoiled little girl, Mayuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.24,0:08:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I've known you since we were kids, \NI'm not lending you money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.55,0:08:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll teach you how harsh life can be...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.10,0:08:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an Upa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.27,0:08:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it rare?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.70,0:08:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not rare, but isn't it cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.21,0:08:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okay, next...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.24,0:08:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.11,0:08:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurisu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.30,0:08:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.77,0:08:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have we met somewhere before?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.22,0:08:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurisu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.63,0:08:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.17,0:08:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.15,0:08:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.37,0:08:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.93,0:09:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.22,0:09:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Nakabachi's press conference
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.51,0:09:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will now begin in the 8th Floor Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.21,0:09:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.19,0:09:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.55,0:09:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I never imagined I'd have to \Npretend to be myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.59,0:09:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kurisu picked up the Upa that Mayuri dropped?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.85,0:09:45.14,Sign24B,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayushii
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.14,0:09:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But now that it's no longer metal,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.81,0:09:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that folder will burn in the airplane accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.62,0:10:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All that's left is getting rid of Nakabachi,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.81,0:10:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and finding a chance to knock out Kurisu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.65,0:10:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The liquid dried up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.12,0:10:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.51,0:10:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I haven't used it for such a long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}air got in and dried out the liquid...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.30,0:10:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.47,0:10:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy, I wanted you to read this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.26,0:10:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Think...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Think!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.64,0:10:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There must be something...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.67,0:10:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Something!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.06,0:10:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Getting rid of Nakabachi won't be difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.36,0:10:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But the blood's problematic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.74,0:10:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If there were just something \NI could substitute...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.25,0:10:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.64,0:10:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you call it stealing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.56,0:10:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.69,0:11:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.71,0:11:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.43,0:11:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A man who desires chaos...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.13,0:11:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One who will reset the world's ruling structure...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.11,0:11:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the man who will destroy your ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.85,0:11:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.94,0:11:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.31,0:11:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hououin Kyouma!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.34,0:11:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're that kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.28,0:11:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.91,0:11:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.81,0:11:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You worked together, \Nto ruin my press conference...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.99,0:11:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... So that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.33,0:11:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.40,0:11:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.40,0:11:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.22,0:12:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.95,0:12:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you bring that knife?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.48,0:12:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.97,0:12:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.40,0:12:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do my godlike powers terrify you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.85,0:12:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't insult me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.52,0:12:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, you're shaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.32,0:12:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.72,0:12:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long will you insult me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.31,0:12:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultimately, you're just a small, pathetic man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.60,0:12:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A man too small to enjoy his \Nown daughter's talent couldn't kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.40,0:12:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I don't have too many J-books, \Nbut I'll take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.94,0:12:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.47,0:12:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.82,0:12:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.13,0:13:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.23,0:13:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.05,0:13:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's what you get...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.82,0:13:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.60,0:13:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Almost there...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.63,0:13:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.05,0:13:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.10,0:13:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.75,0:13:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.16,0:14:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lie down. I'll call an ambulance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.54,0:14:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.64,0:14:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this emergency services?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.89,0:14:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need someone here now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.60,0:14:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.16,0:14:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.68,0:14:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.49,0:15:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is, without doubt,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.07,0:15:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the Kurisu I saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.83,0:15:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.82,0:15:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.40,0:15:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.06,0:15:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you just wait a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.26,0:15:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.20,0:16:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll bleed out...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.04,0:16:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.26,0:16:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Is someone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.36,0:16:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.96,0:16:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're about to begin the longest,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.41,0:16:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}most important three weeks of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.16,0:16:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You went too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.65,0:16:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.80,0:16:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.65,0:16:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The plan succeeded...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.24,0:16:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I can do is stop the bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.33,0:16:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we get back, you need a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.49,0:16:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be hard, but try to hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.23,0:16:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.26,0:17:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.02,0:17:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.29,0:17:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one knows what will happen \Nin the Steins Gate world line.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.60,0:17:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuha...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.75,0:17:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if your theory is correct, the paper will burn, \Nso the time machine race won't come to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.54,0:17:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither will World War III.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.61,0:17:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stay with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.86,0:17:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll say thank you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.87,0:17:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.26,0:17:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,850)}I'll see you in seven years.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.64,0:17:56.60,Sign24A,,0000,0000,0000,,To Okarin
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.64,0:17:56.60,Sign24B,,0000,0000,0000,,For Okabe \NRintarou-sama
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.60,0:17:58.56,Sign24B,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe Rintarou-sama
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.29,0:18:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.63,0:18:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That paper would have altered mankind's future...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.98,0:18:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a paper for constructing a time machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.29,0:18:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's gone... Burned up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.14,0:18:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His words were unclear,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.55,0:18:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the Russian government plans to deny...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.00,0:18:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin was here, Ruka-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.18,0:18:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I missed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.56,0:18:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When he came by...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.63,0:18:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This badge identifies you as Lab Member #006.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.68,0:18:33.26,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When did I become a lab member?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.26,0:18:38.14,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Those memories may rest in your other life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.05,0:18:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are these characters?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.56,0:18:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyouma?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was just here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.97,0:18:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.79,0:18:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get something, Feyris-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.99,0:18:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.89,0:18:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This badge is for Lab Member #007.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.25,0:19:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you desire my aid, hold the badge and say,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.37,0:19:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"La Yohda Stasella."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.82,0:19:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe was just here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.77,0:19:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri-oneechan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.16,0:19:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nae-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.11,0:19:19.06,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll be working here, from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.06,0:19:20.85,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kiryuu Moeka.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.37,0:19:24.14,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,She helped Nae after she fell down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.14,0:19:25.69,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she didn't have a job,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.69,0:19:27.72,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,so she'll be working here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.66,0:19:30.61,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Shiina Mayuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.03,0:19:34.94,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,She's really popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.94,0:19:38.60,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe started hitting on her \Nthe minute he saw her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.16,0:19:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Visit the lab whenever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.48,0:19:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.28,0:19:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.22,0:19:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back-arin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.21,0:19:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you combine "welcome back" and "okarin"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.42,0:20:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.07,0:20:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.39,0:20:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he was going shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.11,0:20:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.41,0:20:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.69,0:20:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said they're lab member badges.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.04,0:20:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lab Member #002 and #003!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.52,0:20:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did we get so many lab members?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.85,0:20:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said they go up to #008.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.06,0:20:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin's "O."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.85,0:20:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina. Hashida. Urushibara. Feyris...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.33,0:20:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are "M" and "K" and "A"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.06,0:20:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.13,0:20:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He had another one that he put in a box.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.85,0:20:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lab Member #008 will arrive in seven years.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.33,0:20:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}More fantasies?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.85,0:20:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's an inevitable future.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.64,0:20:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your inevitable future.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.67,0:20:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.13,0:20:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven years...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.80,0:20:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.65,0:20:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think it'll be?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.42,0:20:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven years... I can't imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.63,0:21:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't think the lab will change.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.09,0:21:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many years go by.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.61,0:21:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.31,0:21:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you writing a paper \Nin an American research lab?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.77,0:21:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you working all night on some experiment?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.73,0:21:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You may still be thinking of your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.60,0:21:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You don't remember the three weeks \Nwe spent together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.66,0:21:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.78,0:21:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right now, you're breathing, speaking,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.93,0:21:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}thinking your hardest about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.29,0:21:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.03,0:21:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're watching the same world I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.78,0:21:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}this world with its unknown future.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.54,0:22:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally found you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.65,0:22:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.71,0:22:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to thank you for saving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.87,0:22:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.71,0:22:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is she here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.32,0:22:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.64,0:22:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I protected her?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.68,0:22:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're flattering me...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.41,0:22:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if that's its choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.47,0:22:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,El Psy Congroo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.85,0:22:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,El Psy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.00,0:22:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We meet again, Christina!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.03,0:22:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you I'm not Christina, \Nand I'm not your assistant...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.89,0:23:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome, my assistant, Makise Kurisu...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.56,0:23:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Christina.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.79,0:23:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No one knows what the future holds.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.25,0:23:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's why its potential is infinite,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.08,0:23:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}just as this meeting demonstrates.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.97,0:23:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fad(1,2622)}This is the choice of Steins Gate.
